flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Receive User<br/>Math Question"]
    B --> C["Discover Available<br/>MCP Tools at Runtime"]
    C --> D["Send Question + Tool List<br/>to LLM"]
    D --> E["LLM Selects Tool<br/>and Extracts Parameters"]
    E --> F{MCP Mode<br/>Enabled?}
    F -->|Yes| G["Invoke MCP-Hosted<br/>Tool with Parameters"]
    F -->|No| H["Invoke Local Embedded<br/>Tool with Parameters"]
    G --> I["Collect Tool Result"]
    H --> I
    I --> J["Return Final Answer<br/>to User"]
    J --> K([End])